    "The data may exist in organized, semi-structured, or unstructured formats.",
    "Robotic Process Automation system is able to successfully retrieve data from the deep web by using deep learning algorithms.",
    "In addition, the mining process may be completed more easily with the use of web analytics, artificial intelligence, and big data analytics.",
    "Department EnablerThe term \"Robots\" is defined and discussed by in relation to RPA.",
